protobuf:run

Full name:

com.github.igor-petruk.protobuf:protobuf-maven-plugin:0.4-SNAPSHOT:run

Description:

(no description)

Attributes:

  • Requires a Maven 2.0 project to be executed.
  • Requires dependency resolution of artifacts in scope: runtime.
  • Binds by default to the lifecycle phase: generate-sources.

Required Parameters

Name Type Since Description
addSources boolean - Should plugin add outputDirectory to sources that are going to be compiled
Default value is: true.
extension String - Default extension for protobuf files
Default value is: .proto.
ignoreVersions boolean - Setting to "true" disables version check between 'protoc' and the protobuf library used by module
Default value is: false.
inputDirectories File[] - Input directories that have *.protoc files (or the configured extension). If none specified then src/main/proto is used.
outputDirectory File - Output directory, that generated java files would be stored
Default value is: ${project.build.directory}/generated-sources/protobuf.

Parameter Details

addSources:

Should plugin add outputDirectory to sources that are going to be compiled
  • Type: boolean
  • Required: Yes
  • Expression: ${run.addSources}
  • Default: true

extension:

Default extension for protobuf files
  • Type: java.lang.String
  • Required: Yes
  • Expression: ${run.extension}
  • Default: .proto

ignoreVersions:

Setting to "true" disables version check between 'protoc' and the protobuf library used by module
  • Type: boolean
  • Required: Yes
  • Expression: ${run.ignoreVersions}
  • Default: false

inputDirectories:

Input directories that have *.protoc files (or the configured extension). If none specified then src/main/proto is used.
  • Type: java.io.File[]
  • Required: Yes
  • Expression: ${run.inputDirectories}

outputDirectory:

Output directory, that generated java files would be stored
  • Type: java.io.File
  • Required: Yes
  • Expression: ${run.outputDirectory}
  • Default: ${project.build.directory}/generated-sources/protobuf
